Text: This lady is the best!!! She is Professional understanding just the best!! Her work is amazing!! I wouldn’t go anywhere else ever!!! I did kick-eyebrows and love them. I walked in to work & everyone asked me where did I go. They have appointments now with Vicki!!

Name: Kimberly Andrews
Text:
I recently had my brows micro bladed. The result was fantastic! I experienced minimal pain in the beginning. However, once the skin was broken that minimal pain subsided immediately. I even fell asleep during the procedure. Ms. Le took great care to precisely map the brow area before beginning the micro blading. The place was comfortable and conveniently located in downtown Oak Lawn. Ms. Le is very kind and skilled at what she does. I recommend her services to everyone!
You should be very happy with the service you receive. I most definitely am! Make your appointment today!

Text: Love Vicky and Nu You Spa! Vicky is professional, friendly, and knowledgeable when it come to the latest beauty techniques, keeping her skills on point. I will definitely continue with Nu You Spa and recommend for self-care pampering.

Name: Yolanda McDonald
Text: I am so pleased with the services that I get from Vicky. I have been coming to her for over a year for my nails, brows, and lashes. I am an extremely picky person about my services. In addition, I have a highly professional job where my appearance is extremely important and Vicky keeps me looking good. She stands behind her work and provides a high quality of work and good products. She is passionate about her work and strives to make sure you are satisfied. Further, she keeps her skills current and can always do the latest techniques. Lastly, she is very clean and provides friendly customer service; I am always highly satisfied when I leave.
